Revision history for Perl module Text::Unidecode

{{$NEXT}}
    * Fixed up test suite to avoid "Wide character in print" warnings
    * Fixed missing variable in debugging sprintf
    * Add unidecode_to_charset() to decode into an arbitrary charset (ascii by default)
    * Allow on-the-fly remapping of transliterations with remap()
    * Encode 2.12 required for coderef support

